{"tid":878740,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]有無頭髮好油既人入黎分享用緊咩洗頭水","createTime":"2018-10-27T11:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T20:04:03.000Z","uid":207604,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"6a37f538d26b45063840449dbd80b399bc99cc7a","tid":878740,"uid":207604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"每次用完一支洗頭水都要換第二支<br />\n但換左十幾支都搵唔到啱用既<br />\n<br />\n拋磚先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/190837_5edbfa8a9cc0f2cfcd83a59762ea3322.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F190837_5edbfa8a9cc0f2cfcd83a59762ea3322.png&h=9a7fc359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用過第一行 紅色 粉紅色 橙色 第三行頭皮同埋紫色<br />\n無一隻可以頂到去第二朝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/191106_ab5bd2100b1e871558cfb8ba67b71019.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F191106_ab5bd2100b1e871558cfb8ba67b71019.png&h=16176311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢支都係廢既 仲衰過lush<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/191219_72993373c31dcb88dd6df7dbbb026d14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F191219_72993373c31dcb88dd6df7dbbb026d14.png&h=b06e63a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢支仲廢過diane個支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/191324_038b0f316c03734a8ff46bf168a191bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F191324_038b0f316c03734a8ff46bf168a191bd.png&h=37a9c405&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廢既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/191433_128c63f37cef2412e44a41de6c452aa8.png\" data